t = int(input())
(a, c) = ([], [])
for i in range(t):
    s = [int(c) for c in input().split()]
    a += s
    if 1900 <= a[0]:
        c.append('Division 1')
        del a[0]
        continue
    elif 1600 <= a[0] <= 1899:
        c.append('Division 2')
        del a[0]
        continue
    elif 1400 <= a[0] <= 1599:
        c.append('Division 3')
        del a[0]
        continue
    else:
        c.append('Division 4')
        del a[0]
        continue
print(*c, sep='\n')
